rows.label: tlk79000005_01_msg0001
rows.name:
No matter the age, you must always
be prepared, lest some conniving rat
stabs you in the back.

rows.label: tlk79000005_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm not referring to anyone in
particular, you understand.

rows.label: tlk79000005_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But it's a story you hear all too often.
I'd advise you to tread very carefully.
